omer registration form » tech tips » our personnel » storage instructions » useful links » purchase order » career » customer feedback form » contact us » media advertisement   product pdf       hp lubes is an integral part of hindustan petroleum corporation limited one of indias frontline oil majors committed to providing energy and fueling growth in every significant area of development in pursuit of this vision there is a sustained emphasis on environment protection and preserving the cultural heritage of india hp lubricants are borne out of an intense and unrelenting r  d effort which aims at producing quality products that enhance automotive performance standards “when we created hindustan petroleum we created a new kind of venture firmone that’s based on teamwork superior service to entrepreneurs and an intense dedication to building technology companies of lasting value” founded in order to serve the needs of automated equipments manufacturers for innovative high quality and reasonably priced antifriction linear bearings we help bring electronics products to the market faster and more cost effectively by providing complete electronic product supply chain management around the world our goal is to achieve customer satisfaction through excellence in design supply chain management manufacturing and repair solutions through our culture our drive and the expertise of each individual employee we are uniquely positioned to provide bestinclass services to a global customer base    alcon  company all rights are reserved developed  managed by get enquiry home  hindustan petroleum corporation limited india skip to main contents  text size  contrast scheme screen reader access login dealervendor tuesday  august  about us   showhide the sub menu overview introduction our roots we believe board of directors governance infrastructure major ongoing projects hpcl recognition and awards jvs  subsidiaries products  services  showhide the sub menu overview refineries aviation bu