y people m k surana ceo chairman managing director products oil natural gas petroleum lubricant petrochemical revenue ₹ crore us billion  operating income ₹ crore us million  net income ₹ crore us million  total assets ₹ crore us billion  owner government of india  number of employees   website wwwhindustanpetroleumcom hindustan petroleum corporation limited hpcl bse  nse hindpetro is an indian stateowned oil and natural gas company with its headquarters at mumbai maharashtra it has about  marketshare in india among publicsector companies psus and a strong marketing infrastructure the government of india owns  shares in hpcl and others are distributed amongst financial institutes public and other investors the company is ranked th on the fortune global  list of the worlds biggest corporations as of  on th of july  the government of india announced the acquisition of hindustan petroleum corporation by oil and natural gas corporation contents  history  operations  products  refineries  international rankings  major facilities  major ongoing projects  subsidiaries  prize petroleum company limited  see also  references  external links historyedit a view of hpcl from yarada hill hpcl was incorporated in  after the takeover and merger of erstwhile esso standard and lube india limited by the esso acquisition of undertakings in india act  caltex oil refining india ltd coril was taken over by the government of india in  and merged with hpcl in  by the corilhpcl amalgamation order  kosan gas company was merged with hpcl in  by the kosangas company acquisition act  in  following a petition by the centre for public interest litigation cpil the supreme court of india restrained the central government from privatising hindustan petroleum and bharat petroleum without the approval of parliament as counsel for the cpil rajinder sachar and prashant bhushan said that the only way to disinvest in the companies would be to repeal or amend the acts by which they were nationalised in the s as a result the government would need a majority in both houses to push through any privatisation hpcl has been steadily growing over the years the refining capacity increased from  million metric tonnes mmt in  to  million metric tonnes as of march  on the financial front the net income form salesoperations grew from in ₹ crores in – to in ₹ crores in financial year – during fy  its net profit was in ₹ crores operationsedit hindustan petroleum fuel pump near town hall coimbatore hpcl operates two major refineries producing a wide variety of petroleum fuels and specialties one in mumbai west coast of  million metric tonnes per annum mmtpa capacity and the other in visakhapatnam east coast with a capacity of  mmtpa hpcl holds an equity stake of  in mangalore refinery and petrochemicals limited mrpl a stateoftheart refinery at mangalore with a capacity of  mmtpa another refinery of  mmtpa set up in bathinda punjab by hmel a joint venture with mittal energy investments pte ltd hpcl has signed a memorandum of understanding with the government of rajasthan for setting up a refinery near barmer it would be operated under a joint venture company jvc called hpclrajasthan refinery limited hpcl also owns and operates the largest lubricant refinery in india producing lube base oils of international standards with a capacity of  tmt this refinery accounts for over  of indias total lube base oil production presently hpcl produces over  grades of lubes specialities and greases the marketing network of hpcl consists of  zonal offices in major cities and  regional offices facilitated by a supply and distribution infrastructure comprising terminals aviation service facilities liquefied petroleum gas lpg bottling plants lube filling plants inland relay depots retail outlets petrol pumps and lpg and lube distributorships hpcl has stateoftheart information technology infrastructure to support its core business the data center is at hitech city in hyderabad productsedit this section may be confusing or unclear to readers please help us clarify the section there might be a discussion about this on the talk page october  learn how and when to remove this template message am hp petrol pump in khammam hp cooking gas delivery vehicle petrol is known as motor spirit in the oil industry hpcl markets the product through its retail pumps all over india its principle consumers are personal vehicle owners diesel is known as high speed diesel in the oil industry hpcl markets the products through its retail pumps as well as terminals and depots its consumers are regular auto owners transport agencies industries etc lubricants hpcl is the market leader in lubricants and associated products it commands over  of market share in this sector the popular brands of hp lubes are laal ghoda hp milcy thanda raja koolgard racer liquified petroleum gas the hpcl brand of lpg is a popular brand across india for domestic and industrial uses aviation turbine fuel with major air service facilities in all major airports of india hpcl is a key player in this sector supplying atf to major airlines it has an accomplishment of sorts to supply fuel to us emulsions refineriesedit hp oil refinery in visakhapatnam hpcl has a number of refineries in india some are listed below mumbai refinery  million metric tonnes mmt capacity visakhapatnam refinery  mmt at visakhapatnam mangalore refinery pvt ltd  mmt at mangalore karnataka hpcl has a  stake guru gobind singh refinery  mmt at bathinda punjab hpcl and mittal energy each have a  stake barmer refinery  mmt capacity it is a joint venture with the rajasthan government international rankingsedit hpcl is a fortune global  company as per the ranking of  and was ranked at position  hpcl has been ranked at position  as per the latest ranking of  hpcl was featured on the forbes global  list for  at position  it was the th most valuable brand in india according to an annual survey conducted by brand finance and the economic times in  major facilitiesedit scindia road near hpcl mumbai refinery fuel and lubes vizag refinery fuel mangalore mrpl batinda hmel silvassa lube stateoftheart plant for grease and specialities one of the most advanced fully automated installations in asia lube  grease mfg facility mazagaon mumbai lpg storage cavern one of the biggest storage facilities of lpg in asia at vizag—salpg pipelines mbpl mpspl mdpl vvspl several terminals  depots many lpg bottling plants major ongoing projectsedit rewari kanpur pipeline mangalorebangalore lpg pipeline mhmspl pipeline visakh refinery modernization project subsidiariesedit prize petroleum company limitededit prize petroleum company limited prize is the wholly owned subsidiary of hindustan petroleum corporation limited hpcl prize is focused on the appraisal and development of hydrocarbon accumulations in the onshore and offshore projects by conducting exploration development and production of petroleum and other activities in accordance with its mission prizes operating projects are the hirapur marginal oil fields of cambay basin near gandhinagar gujarat under a service contract with ongc and the prenelp production sharing contract psc for the sanganpur mehsana field with ms hydrocarbon development company p ltd hdcpl as operator recently prize signed a sale and purchase agreement to acquire nonoperated minority stake in two gas assets in offshore south australia hpcl biofuels limited credahpcl biofuels limited hpcl rajasthan refinery limited hpcl also facilitating the hp drive track plus cards for purchase of their products and providing the cash back as per the govtcash back offers hpcl also in hp gas for the domestic and industrial gas having major market share in india see alsoedit rajiv gandhi institute of petroleum technology referencesedit  a b c d e hpcl annual report cnbc tv   sustainability report  pdf  p  retrieved  may    httpdpenicinpublicationslistofmaharatnanavratnaandminiratna navratna  fortune global  list cnn money retrieved  